Kimberly Hebert Gregory https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kimberly_Hebert_Gregory 0 Kimberly Hébert Gregory (born December 7, 1973) is an American actress. She began her career in theatre before her breakthrough role as Dr. Belinda Brown in the HBO comedy series Vice Principals in 2016.
